Version: 1.1.0
Copyright (c) 2024. OCX Consortium (https://3docx.org)

Starting ocxtools...
ocxtools >: help

Documented commands (type help <topic>):
========================================
clear  docker  validate  version

Undocumented commands:
======================
exit  help  quit


ocxtools >:

````
## Shell Completion
Command completion is not supported on Windows installations.

